498
00:38:52,913 --> 00:38:54,998
How about it?
Think you can you manage?

499
00:38:55,082 --> 00:38:58,418
A- one and a-two and a-three and...

500
00:38:58,419 --> 00:39:00,962
[plays Jingle Bells off-key]

501
00:39:05,217 --> 00:39:08,386
- Next!
- Fantastic!

502
00:39:08,387 --> 00:39:12,390
