00:40:42,398 --> 00:40:45,733
- [roars]
- [all gasp]

532
00:40:45,818 --> 00:40:48,862
I'm very sorry
for the inconvenience, sir.

533
00:40:48,946 --> 00:40:52,907
Take him home first.
And apologise again!

534
00:40:52,992 --> 00:40:56,995
Be careful with Sandy Claws
when you fetch him! Treat him nicely!

535
00:40:56,996 --> 00:41:00,665
- Got it!
- We'll get it right next time!

536
00:41:00,666 --> 00:41:04,544
You will be a decided improvement

537
00:41:04,628 --> 00:41:07,088
over that treacherous Sally.

538
00:41:07,173 --> 00:41:11,926
Master! The plans.

539
00:41:15,556 --> 00:41:18,391
Excellent, Igor.

